(What This Topic Means) Tj
T*
(Classification groups organisms based on shared features and relationships. In Biology,) Tj
T*
(students do better when they understand not only the definition of Classification, but) Tj
T*
(also the language, symbols, and patterns that appear whenever this topic is tested.) Tj
